How to test jbuf (ingress packages)
===================================
1. Add bridge interface linked to your ethernet interface.
sudo ip link add ifb2 type ifb || :
sudo ip link set ifb2 up
sudo tc qdisc add dev enp1s0 handle ffff: ingress
sudo tc filter add dev enp1s0 parent ffff: u32 match u32 0 0 action mirred egress redirect dev ifb2

2. Activate jitter
sudo tc qdisc add dev ifb2 root netem delay 100ms 50ms

3. Deactivate jitter
sudo tc qdisc del dev ifb2 root

4. See/Use jbuf.plot to generate plots!


How to test jbuf (egress packages)
==================================
1. Add network emulator to your ethernet interface via traffic control
sudo tc qdisc add dev <NET-IF> root handle 1:0 netem delay <TIME>ms <JITTER>ms <CORRELATION>%

2. To remove the jitter again
sudo tc qdisc del dev <NET-IF> root handle 1:0

3. See man tc-netem for more information and different configuration
